#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:2
msgid "桥接检测（Bridge）"
msgstr "Bridge Inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:6
msgid "独立检测相邻引脚 / 焊点之间的连锡（短路）。"
msgstr ""
"Standalone inspection for solder bridges (short circuits) between adjacent "
"leads or solder joints."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the tool's "
"parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:-1
msgid "模板编辑器中的桥接检测元件示例"
msgstr "Example of a Bridge inspection component in the Template Editor"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:18
msgid "**参数说明**"
msgstr "**Parameters**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:20
msgid ""
"**桥接颜色公式（Bridge Color Formula）**：选择用于识别连锡的颜色公式（如 ``2B-R-G``）；选择三色时配置 **三色"
" X / Y / Z / A**。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge Color Formula**: choose the color formula used to detect solder "
"bridges (e.g. ``2B-R-G``); when **Three-color** is chosen, configure "
"**Three-color X / Y / Z / A**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:21
msgid "**值范围（Value Range）**：``2B-R-G`` 等公式的阈值范围（0–100），落入该范围的像素被检出。"
msgstr ""
"**Value Range**: the threshold range (0–100) for formulas such as "
"``2B-R-G``; pixels whose value falls in this band are flagged."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:22
msgid "**灵敏度（Sensitivity）**：桥接颜色检测灵敏度（0–1），值越大检测范围越大。"
msgstr ""
"**Sensitivity**: sensitivity of the bridge color detection (0–1). Higher "
"values widen the detection band."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:23
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：显示桥接检测中间结果。"
msgstr ""
"**Enable Visualization**: display the intermediate results of the bridge "
"detection."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:26
msgid "**常见问题与提示**"
msgstr "**Common questions and tips**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:30
msgid "**连锡敏感度怎么调**：**灵敏度** 值小（接近 0）时只抽蓝色焊锡像素，敏感度大时会把红色 / 偏红的像素也包含进来。先小后大微调。"
msgstr ""
"**How to tune the bridge sensitivity**: when **Sensitivity** is low (close "
"to 0), only blue solder pixels are picked up; raising it adds red or "
"reddish pixels as well. Start low and increase gradually."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/bridge.rst:31
msgid "**电容 / 电阻连锡专用检测**：可把 **桥接检测** 工具独立放置在元件旁，作为附加检测项。"
msgstr ""
"**Dedicated bridge inspection for capacitors and resistors**: place the "
"**Bridge** tool next to the component as a separate inspection item."
